@Comment:	Chi and Mot are the only participants , and the meal lasts about 9 minutes. Mot keeps asking what do in school , and Chi initially says she can't talk while she's eating! So the situation seems a little forced. Nevertheless , Chi is very verbal , and conversation flows along pretty well. Well , MOT has a little trouble keeping Chi at the table. A few times Chi said that Mot said she could do or have something , but that's not exactly what Mot had said.... Tape may have been on voice activation , since there are several cuts.
